# stack-freezed — freezed + json_serializable

## What it is

Codegen for immutable data classes + sealed unions + JSON serialization.

## When I choose it

Every domain model and DTO.

## Conventions I follow

- @freezed sealed classes for state unions (Loading | Data | Error).
- Always implements toJson/fromJson via @JsonSerializable inside the @freezed class.
- Run build_runner watch in dev terminal.

## Common gotchas

- build_runner gets stuck — `flutter pub run build_runner clean && build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs`.
- Don't put logic in freezed classes (use extension methods or plain functions).

## Resources

- pub.dev/packages/freezed



